title: Quentin Tarantino Protests Police Brutality in New York
text:
Quentin Tarantino Protests Police Bru... Quentin Tarantino Protests Police Brutality in New York Next Story Prev Story 8 hrs ago Read more: Hollywood Reporter 
Academy Award-winning filmmaker Quentin Tarantino joined hundreds of demonstrators waving signs, shouting through megaphones and marching along the city's streets on Saturday to protest police brutality nationwide. "I'm a human being with a conscience," said Tarantino, who flew in from California for the event.   Hollywood Reporter.
